name: arcnearby
description: Generate bounding box around center point and search ArcGIS REST service for features within it, sorted by distance

author.name: Tim Wisniewski, Sarah Cordivano, David Walk

readme:
ArcNearby
=========
Generates a bounding box around a center point, queries an ArcGIS REST service to get the features within it, and sorts the results by distance from the center point
